    public class Renderer

      • getPlacemarkVisibility

        protected static boolean getPlacemarkVisibility(Feature feature)
        Gets the visibility of the placemark if it is specified. A visibility value of "1" corresponds as "true", a visibility value of "0" corresponds as false. If the visibility is not set, the method returns "true".
        Parameters:
        feature - Feature to obtain visibility from.
        Returns:
        False if a Feature has a visibility value of "1", true otherwise.
